article_id:3264,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding Issues with the Double-Drops and Half-Stamina Event,image_path:,message:<div>We have confirmed the following issues with the double-drops and half-stamina event that began around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648015200"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>・The drops from main campaign chapter 8 quests on all difficulties are not doubled and the required stamina is not half of the usual amount.</div><div><br></div><div>・The drops from main campaign chapter 7 quests on all difficulties are doubled and the required stamina is half of the usual amount, even though chapter 7 quests are not part of this event.</div><div><br></div><div>As a token of our appreciation for your understanding, we will be sending a gift of 10 exquisite honey to all players who started playing before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648015200"></span>. This gift can be claimed from your goodie box for up to 7 days after reception.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1648185300,update_time1648184670